# Basic API Testing Examples
# 基础 API 测试示例
#
# 使用方法:
# rupost test examples/basic-api.http --env dev
# rupost test examples/basic-api.http --env prod --var api_key=custom-key

### 1. 简单的 GET 请求
# 获取用户列表
GET {{base_url}}/{{api_version}}/users
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. 带查询参数的 GET 请求
# 分页获取用户
GET {{base_url}}/{{api_version}}/users?page=1&limit=10
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. 带认证的 GET 请求
# 获取当前用户信息
GET {{base_url}}/{{api_version}}/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. POST 请求 - JSON Body
# 创建新用户
POST {{base_url}}/{{api_version}}/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}

{
  "email": "{{test_user_email}}",
  "password": "{{test_user_password}}",
  "name": "Test User"
}

###

### 5. PUT 请求 - 更新资源
# 更新用户信息
PUT {{base_url}}/{{api_version}}/users/123
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}

{
  "name": "Updated Name",
  "email": "updated@example.com"
}

###

### 6. DELETE 请求
# 删除用户
DELETE {{base_url}}/{{api_version}}/users/123
Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}

###

### 7. 带自定义 Headers
# 测试带多个自定义 Header 的请求
GET {{base_url}}/{{api_version}}/data
Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}
X-Request-ID: test-request-001
X-Client-Version: 1.0.0
Accept: application/json
Accept-Language: zh-CN

###
